data.description: Spacious, Fully Equipped & On The Lake in Kissimmee Community of Brighton LakesAs the title states, this home is very spacious with over 3400 sq. ft. of living area, and located in one of Kissimmee's best communities with easy access to Pleasant Hill, 17/92 and Poinciana Blvd. The Property and Community feature:* 5 bed 3 Bath with 3461 Sq. Ft.* Open Floor Plan with Kitchen Great Room Combo* Tile & Laminate in Most of the House* Tiled Garage & Lanai* Open Kitchen with Stainless Steel Appliances & Granite Countertops* Backs up to Lake* Fully Fenced* 3 Car Garage* Community Pool, Basketball & Tennis CourtsFor more information or to schedule a showing please contact Jose at 407.230.0900.$50 dollar application sheets, Deposit based on Application Outcome.This property is professionally managed by Premier Estate Agency, LLCFor this and other great properties please visit www.PremierEstateAgency.com
